title: Super Bowl Spread, Total Holding Steady Despite Heavy Action on Seahawks, Over

sources.name: Yahoo Sports NFL
sources.title: Super Bowl Spread, Total Holding Steady Despite Heavy Action on Seahawks, Over
sources.description: The spread moved early to Seattle -4 and -4.5 where it has stayed since, while the total has held at 45.5 after quickly dropping from 46 or higher.
